  <steps>
    <step order="1">Author 3 synthetic test fixtures: `synthetic-nda.txt`, `synthetic-patent.txt`, `synthetic-invoice.txt`. Each ~500-1500 chars with clear domain markers (NDA: "DISCLOSING PARTY", "RECEIVING PARTY", "CONFIDENTIAL INFORMATION"; Patent: "CLAIMS", "INVENTOR", "ABSTRACT"; Invoice: "INVOICE NUMBER", "DUE DATE", "LINE ITEMS").</step>
