    <step order="4">Author test 3: upload synthetic invoice → assert routing selects extract-invoice → assert invoice output schema fields emitted (vendor, customer, lineItems, totals).</step>
    <step order="5">Add cross-validation: confirm task 123 streaming regression test still passes (re-run as part of Phase 6 suite).</step>
    <step order="6">Run `dotnet test tests/integration/Sprk.Bff.Api.IntegrationTests/Services/Ai/Phase6/`. All must pass.</step>
